    "description": "<p>Halflings gain a +1 bonus to all attack rolls when using missile weapons, a +1 bonus to individual initiative, and a -2 AC bonus when attacked by creatures larger than man-sized.</p><p>A creature is considered larger than man-sized if its description includes terms like \"giant,\" \"gargantuan,\" or \"enormous.\" Additionally, real-world creatures that the DM deems larger than a human (such as a horse) also fall into this category. As a general guideline, any non-humanoid creature without a specified size can be assumed to be larger than man-sized if it has 4 or more Hit Dice (HD).</p>",
